headline: New Study Rates Regions Bank Tops in Customer Satisfaction Among Traditional Banks
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., May 22, 2025--Regions Bank on Thursday announced the company was rated number one in customer satisfaction among traditional banks according to the American Customer Satisfaction Index (ACSI®) 2025 Finance and Insurance Study.1
